README.rst: Comprehendable deprecation warning.

The sentence can be misunderstood easily as it does not elaborate that
GeoModelSerializer does not need to be implemented if you're using
ver 0.9.3.

It misleads the user into thinking that it has been deprecated for good.
Closes https://github.com/djangonauts/django-rest-framework-gis/issues/156
